_source.moment_description: A man is playing a flute in front of a microphone.
A small group of people are seen on a stage getting their instruments ready.
An introduction comes onto the screen for a video about skate boarding tricks.
There's a man in a brown shirt bowling in a large alley in a competition with spectators watching him.
On the second attempt, he knocks down more pins and finally gets a spare.
man is standing inside a court practicing a shot put.
A few other men are shown playing guitars as they sit.
One man is playing drums while the others are on flute and guitar.
The lights move fluidly as they crescendo, and they screen goes black.
A woman begins playing the drums while another plays piano and the others watch.
The two continue to play their instruments and others on the side watch.
women are in a gymnastics competition doing high jumps in a roofed gym with a lot of people gathered around them watching them.
woman is painting in a white paper green leaves in a chinese tree.
a red paint is shown and woman put a stamp on the corner of the paper.
A credit comes onto the screen introducing the grad finale trick.
The closing credits then com onto the screen to end the video.
The man does a trick and lands with one foot on the board.
Then after he continues bowling, the pins knock down the remaining pins down.
He bowls again and knocks down four pins.
A camera shows various shots of a man standing on a string and trying to keep his balance.
More boys continue balancing on the string with several others being interviewed by the camera.
Another man trows a disc.
woman is painting a blue ad purple chinese flower.
a red and black flowers are painted on a white paper with very detail for the same woman in a dark room.
The opening credits are shown for a video about bowling.
Skateboarder to different tricks spinning their boards.
People sit by a building and watch friends skateboard.
The skateboarder rubs the top of his grip tape with his hand.
The video ends with the closing captions shown on the screen.
A man is seen cleaning off a bowling ball and leads into several clips of him bowling down a lane.
More shots are shown of the man bowling while the camera captures him from several angles.
Then when he hits the ball again, he knocks down four pins in the first attempt.
Next the screen  flashes to a younger male jerking and then drops the bar on the ground.
Several more people are shown lifting weights and dropping them on the ground.
More feet are shown trying to balance on the string with a man talking to the camera and others showing how to set it up.
A person is seen close up walking on a rope and jumping.
A man speaks to the camera while showing more clips of people walking on a rope.
Many people speak to the camera as the people continue to walk and perform tricks on the rope.
The group plays for the audience, occasionally zooming in on individuals.
participants are on the podium receiveng thei medals.
woman used some black painting for make details, put the red stamp on the corner and finished the painting with yellow and reddetails on the flowers.
The video then shows several bowlers doing bowling tricks at a bowling alley.
A man throws the ball and simultaneously throws himself down the alley as well.
The skateboards miss their tricks and catch themselves.
Several tricks are shown while someone narrates the tricks.
A man is shown on the screen giving details about the tricks and offering pointers and tips.
He begins by picking up his blue bowling ball and then, holds it firmly to shoot it at the pins.
He gets a strike after the ball hits the pin.
He continues throwing the ball several times and every time he gets a strike.
The crowd cheers for him as he bowls the ball again knocking down two more pins.
He raises his hands feeling victorious.
A man is standing in a gym preparing to lift a set of weights placed on a bar.
The man begins to dance as he lifts and drops the bar and the continuation of weightlifting is repeated.
After,the men continue walking around the gym eating a protein bar.
The men tighten the rope and show more people walking and juggling.
a man is in a racetrack doing a shot put with a lot of people around him watching him.
man is in a practicing field practicing a shot put on sunny day.
man is doing a javeling throw in a big large field.
men are praticing shot puts and javelin throws on fields.
A man is standing behind a fence practicing with a heavy ball on his shoulder.
Several men are shown in various throwing sports.
A man throws a spear.
